Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.31,0:00:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona Nanoka, saat kau di sisi lain,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.19,0:00:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}apa kau bisa bertemu shikigami
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.28,0:00:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang dikirim Tuan Mao?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.99,0:00:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.24,0:00:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga meluangkan waktu\Nuntuk memikirkan semuanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.50,0:00:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mao, ke mana kau membawa kami?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.21,0:00:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ryounkaku,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.96,0:00:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}juga dikenal sebagai Menara Asakusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.13,0:00:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ryounkaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.71,0:00:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita melewatinya\Nsaat tiba di Ibu Kota Kekaisaran.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.63,0:00:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu bangunan yang megah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.85,0:01:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.85,0:01:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini Ryounkaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.10,0:01:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kondisinya buruk.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Otoya.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.24,0:01:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, Tuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.46,0:01:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu cahaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.80,0:01:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Mao.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.76,0:01:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu benda terkutuk untuk menarik ayakashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.14,0:01:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.65,0:01:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makhluk-makhluk itu
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.94,0:01:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}berasal dari gempa itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.33,0:02:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Otoya!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.20,0:02:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.50,0:02:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah kuduga kau akan datang\Nuntuk membunuhku!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.13,0:02:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak peduli siapa yang mendatangiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.93,0:02:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan menyerang mereka!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.65,0:03:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kukira itu mustahil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.69,0:04:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi apa kau
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.74,0:04:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hyakka, murid senior?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.16,0:04:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tampak agak berbeda, tapi…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.58,0:04:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah kau
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.99,0:04:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mao, si pengkhianat?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.66,0:04:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pengkhianat?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena kau, kami…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka datang!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.93,0:04:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hyakka, katakan apa yang terjadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.64,0:04:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pedang itu…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.18,0:04:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu Pedang Hagunsei?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.23,0:04:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.56,0:04:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini diberikan kepadaku oleh guru kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.40,0:04:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pedang ini melambangkan
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.86,0:04:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bahwa kau penerusku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.16,0:04:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mao.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.83,0:04:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kupercayakan
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.04,0:04:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}semua gulungan rahasia\Nyang diwariskan turun-temurun kepadamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.46,0:04:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku penerusnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.42,0:05:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi pedang ini…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.10,0:05:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mao.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.51,0:05:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau senang menerima pedang itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.43,0:05:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona Sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.52,0:05:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak. Kau tidak sebodoh itu, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.82,0:05:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.23,0:05:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menerima Pedang Hagunsei\Ntak perlu dirayakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.32,0:05:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini pedang pertanda buruk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak tahu
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.08,0:05:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pedang Hagunsei adalah pedang yang tangguh
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.17,0:05:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan bahkan bisa menangkis\Nserangan Hyakka Agung.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.79,0:05:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.34,0:05:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku belum pernah melihat\Nseseorang memberi dirinya gelar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.30,0:05:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah lama tinggal di dunia ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.55,0:05:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi itu mungkin kali pertama,\Nbahkan bagiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.72,0:05:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pedang terkutuk itu
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.89,0:05:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sia-sia di tanganmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.43,0:05:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku belum selesai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.39,0:05:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu milikku!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.15,0:06:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hyakka! Jangan sentuh pedang itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.95,0:06:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.91,0:06:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika orang selain Mao atau aku\Nmenyentuh pedang itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.58,0:06:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}racun dari darah Byoki\Nakan memasuki tubuh mereka dan…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.13,0:06:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hyakka!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.55,0:06:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia mati.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.89,0:06:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Dia mati?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.56,0:06:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mao! Kemarilah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.77,0:06:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Datanglah ke arahku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.31,0:06:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, Hyakka.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.36,0:06:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.57,0:06:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah jelas dia mengubur sesuatu di sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.86,0:06:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin itu benda terkutuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.12,0:06:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa? Berjalanlah ke arahku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.04,0:06:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia ingin aku menginjaknya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.79,0:07:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah. Aku datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.67,0:07:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.97,0:07:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana? Cukup keren, bukan, Mao?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.18,0:07:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sangat mengesankan, Hyakka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.31,0:07:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu memang mengesankan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.43,0:07:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Apa?\N- Gawat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.10,0:07:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padamkan apinya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.90,0:07:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hyakka!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.36,0:07:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Dasar bodoh!\N- Aduh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.94,0:07:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia dimarahi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.36,0:07:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Selalu saja kau!\N- Maaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.95,0:07:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia seniormu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.66,0:07:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.87,0:07:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Penampilannya sedikit berubah,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.66,0:07:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi sikap dan tekniknya\Nsama seperti dahulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.83,0:07:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu jelas Hyakka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.75,0:07:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa dia hidup di zaman ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.34,0:07:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa dia benar-benar mati?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.30,0:07:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya. Dia mengembuskan napas terakhirnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.84,0:07:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku punya banyak pertanyaan untuknya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.39,0:07:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sayang sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.02,0:08:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Mao. Apa yang harus kita lakukan\Ndengan jasadnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.56,0:08:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Haruskah kita menguburnya?\N- Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.02,0:08:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Otoya! Itu seperti membuang mayat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.81,0:08:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Membuang mayat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.57,0:08:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya! Itu salah besar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.57,0:08:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kukira aku sudah mati!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.13,0:08:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau handuk?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.21,0:08:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.00,0:08:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia sombong sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.35,0:08:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi dia sangat pendek.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.14,0:08:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, kau senior Mao.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.23,0:08:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi bukankah kau lebih muda darinya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.44,0:08:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memangnya kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.10,0:08:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hyakka memulai latihannya\Nsepuluh hari sebelum aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.57,0:08:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berarti aku seniornya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.24,0:08:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mengerti.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.53,0:08:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti dalam komedi, yang mulai\Nlebih dahulu adalah senior, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.12,0:09:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nanoka mulai lagi\Ndengan interpretasi anehnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.37,0:09:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.16,0:09:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kau masih hidup selama ini seperti Mao?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.79,0:09:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hampir mati berkali-kali.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.59,0:09:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi di sinilah aku, masih hidup.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.72,0:09:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.01,0:09:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kau tak bisa mati?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.97,0:09:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.43,0:09:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat dia menyentuh Pedang Hagunsei tadi,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.22,0:09:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hyakka jelas sudah mati.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.23,0:09:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak seperti aku\Nyang menyatu dengan tubuh Byoki,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.52,0:09:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ada sesuatu yang berbeda.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.07,0:09:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tahu, Mao…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.19,0:09:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau pikir Guru menyukaimu, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.53,0:09:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.99,0:09:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pernahkah kau melihat
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.12,0:09:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}wajah Guru?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.25,0:09:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wajahnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.13,0:09:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sisi kanan wajah Guru
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.04,0:09:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}selalu disembunyikan topeng.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.17,0:09:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entah itu cedera atau bekas penyakit,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.59,0:09:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dia tidak pernah melepaskannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.68,0:10:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pernah melihatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.85,0:10:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak lama setelah dia menunjukmu\Nsebagai penerus.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.14,0:10:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia memanggil\Naku dan beberapa murid senior lainnya
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.86,0:10:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ke Goshikido di dekat pinggiran kamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.57,0:10:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Goshikido memiliki lima dinding,\Nmasing-masing dengan pintu masuk sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.57,0:10:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu dibangun sedemikian rupa\Nagar kami bisa masuk tanpa saling melihat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.33,0:10:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak tahu siapa lagi yang dipanggil
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.66,0:10:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}karena bagian dalamnya dipisahkan dinding.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.09,0:10:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti yang kalian tahu,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.05,0:10:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}banyak seni rahasia\Nyang diwariskan di Klan Goko
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.76,0:10:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}berasal dari tradisi Jugondo,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.26,0:10:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bentuk sihir jujutsu\Nyang dilarang di zaman sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.27,0:10:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu tidak hanya mencakup mantra membunuh,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.60,0:10:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi juga mantra pembangkitan\Narwah orang mati,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.06,0:10:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan mantra rahasia\Nuntuk memanipulasi umur sesuka hati.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.69,0:10:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku memutuskan\Nuntuk memberikan semuanya kepada Mao.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.32,0:11:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ada yang keberatan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.54,0:11:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.04,0:11:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.79,0:11:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa Mao?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.75,0:11:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah karena dia berbakat?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.84,0:11:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, dia tidak pernah\Nmenganggapnya serius.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.38,0:11:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia hampir tidak bisa\Nmerapal satu mantra pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.39,0:11:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.64,0:11:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak pernah peduli dengan kutukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.14,0:11:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika ada di antara kalian\Nyang yakin layak mewarisi seni rahasia,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.65,0:11:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kutuk Mao sampai mati.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.32,0:11:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lima orang yang berkumpul di sini\Nakan saling bertarung
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}demi hak mewarisi seni rahasia.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.99,0:11:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa pun yang selamat pada akhirnya
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.20,0:11:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}akan menjadi penerus sejati.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.24,0:11:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika kau tidak punya tekad\Nuntuk melakukan itu…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.37,0:11:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}matilah di sini!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.75,0:11:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitulah seni rahasia Jugondo\Ndiwariskan turun-temurun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.51,0:12:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga selamat\Ndari pertarungan kutukan mematikan
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.14,0:12:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan menjadi yang terakhir bertahan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.06,0:12:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mao dipersembahkan kepada kalian semua\Nsebagai korban.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.65,0:12:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mao dipersembahkan kepada kalian semua\Nsebagai korban.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.33,0:12:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ditakdirkan menjadi
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.87,0:12:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}korban?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.62,0:12:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lima murid senior seharusnya mengutuk Mao,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.21,0:12:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan siapa pun yang membunuhnya\Nlebih dahulu akan menang?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.50,0:12:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu mengerikan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.84,0:12:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.88,0:12:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}di peringkat terendah\Ndi antara banyak muridnya,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.55,0:12:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan aku berlatih jauh lebih sedikit\Ndaripada yang lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.34,0:12:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi anehnya Guru menyukaimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.64,0:12:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski kau hampir tidak bisa\Nmenggunakan jujutsu paling dasar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.23,0:12:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mao.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.35,0:12:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kupercayakan padamu semua gulungan rahasia\Nyang diwariskan turun-temurun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.32,0:12:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa Mao?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.86,0:13:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia tidak layak.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.44,0:13:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kecemburuan, kebencian…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.45,0:13:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Emosi negatif berputar di sekelilingku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.82,0:13:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Guru mengatakannya sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.66,0:13:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk mewarisi banyak kutukan rahasia,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.91,0:13:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}seseorang harus memiliki
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.37,0:13:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}energi yang lahir dari emosi gelap.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.29,0:13:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejak awal,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.30,0:13:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Guru mungkin berniat menjadikanmu korban.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.93,0:13:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mungkin hanya tidak tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.59,0:13:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, itu alasan
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.97,0:13:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Guru memberikan Pedang Hagunsei
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.02,0:13:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kepadaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.69,0:13:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa maksudmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.56,0:13:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hyakka pasti sudah tahu, tapi…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.98,0:13:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.90,0:13:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hagunsei adalah
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.57,0:13:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bintang ketujuh
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.57,0:13:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dari Bintang Biduk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.24,0:13:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bintang jahat yang konon membawa sial
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.36,0:13:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ke segala arah yang ditunjuknya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.87,0:13:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.41,0:13:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, saat diberi pedang ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.04,0:13:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku bertanya-tanya, kenapa mempercayakan\Nsesuatu yang membawa sial kepadaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.04,0:14:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.55,0:14:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya. Hagunsei.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.71,0:14:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu soal itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.92,0:14:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia tidak tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.76,0:14:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itukah alasannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.68,0:14:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sadar telah dikutuk,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.47,0:14:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan sebelum kami sempat\Nmengutukmu sampai mati,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.18,0:14:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kau bekerja sama dengan Byoki?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.19,0:14:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bekerja sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.06,0:14:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.69,0:14:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu kesalahpahaman.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.40,0:14:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mao, mungkinkah kau tidak tahu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.28,0:14:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita dijebak.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.49,0:14:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau dan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.58,0:14:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hyakka.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.29,0:14:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mao, setahuku,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.67,0:14:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku tidak peduli\Napakah guru gila kita sudah mati
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.50,0:14:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}atau kediamannya hancur.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.18,0:14:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.80,0:14:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kenapa kau harus membunuh Nona Sana juga?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.68,0:14:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu satu hal yang tidak bisa kumaafkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.64,0:14:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona Sana…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.15,0:15:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona Sana?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.02,0:15:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.36,0:15:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudmu Tuan Mao membunuhnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.44,0:15:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu kata para murid senior.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.78,0:15:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak ingin melihat wajahmu lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.32,0:15:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah muak!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.12,0:15:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku membunuh
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.41,0:15:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona Sana?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.87,0:15:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anu…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.50,0:15:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa Nona Sana?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.51,0:15:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia putri Guru.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.09,0:15:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia membunuhnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.22,0:15:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa Mao
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.97,0:15:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}memang membunuh wanita itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.14,0:15:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hari itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.64,0:15:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}apa yang kulakukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak ingat apa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.15,0:15:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mao.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.20,0:15:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masing-masing hanya dua nasi kepal…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.36,0:15:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kudengar ada gadis muda lain\Nyang menghilang.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.62,0:15:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin dia pindah ke penampungan lain?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.37,0:15:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, rumornya,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.16,0:16:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}putra Tuan Ibaraki, pria yang mengizinkan\Nkita tinggal di sini,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.92,0:16:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bertanggung jawab atas insiden itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.75,0:16:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga mendengar rumor itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.84,0:16:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bahkan sebelum gempa bumi,\Nmereka bilang dia selalu membuat masalah
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.80,0:16:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan keluarga itu menutupinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.48,0:16:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuchinawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.69,0:16:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.81,0:16:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Tanehiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.86,0:16:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau melakukannya lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.23,0:16:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau melakukannya lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.36,0:16:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini menjadi topik pembicaraan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.91,0:16:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bahkan setelah semua kekacauan\Nakibat gempa bumi besar itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.12,0:16:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan khawatir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.24,0:16:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pasti akan memilih gadis\Ntanpa ikatan keluarga.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.62,0:16:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gadis itu bilang\Nitu kali pertama dia mengisi perutnya
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.29,0:16:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dengan nasi putih.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.51,0:16:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia tampak sangat senang.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.76,0:16:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku yakin dia mati dengan sangat puas.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.47,0:16:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selain itu, Kuchinawa,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.80,0:17:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku bisa tenang mengetahui\Nkau akan membersihkan semuanya untukku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.77,0:17:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, Tuan Tanehiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.24,0:17:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebelum gempa bumi besar,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.81,0:17:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ini rumah kaca yang indah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.00,0:17:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.86,0:17:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau pantas mendapatkan\Ntempat peristirahatan yang lebih indah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.05,0:17:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudmu, kau tak tahu, Uozumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.13,0:17:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bahkan tentang Nona Sana?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.43,0:17:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku diciptakan jauh setelahnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.81,0:17:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak tahu apa pun
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.43,0:17:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tentang masa muda Tuan Mao.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.65,0:17:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf membuatmu menunggu, Shiraha.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.57,0:17:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak apa-apa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.53,0:17:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamarmu memiliki nuansa retro\Nyang menggemaskan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.86,0:17:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menurutmu begitu? Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.36,0:17:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin bertanya tentang Jugondo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.12,0:18:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik. Jugondo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.33,0:18:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Secara umum,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.54,0:18:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}itu seni medis yang menggunakan jujutsu\Nuntuk melindungi orang
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.50,0:18:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dari energi jahat\Nyang diyakini menyebabkan penyakit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.29,0:18:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seni medis?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.21,0:18:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pada era Nara,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.46,0:18:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}di bawah sistem pemerintahan Ritsuryo,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.26,0:18:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ada biro medis bernama Tenyakuryo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.84,0:18:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Para penyihir Jugon\Nmenjadi pejabat pemerintah resmi di sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.68,0:18:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sementara mereka menggunakan jujutsu\Nuntuk mengobati penyakit,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.77,0:18:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mereka juga bisa menggunakan kodoku,\Nyang memanfaatkan makhluk beracun,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.73,0:18:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan Enmi, yang memakai boneka kutukan\Nuntuk membunuh orang.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.40,0:18:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana mereka terhubung dengan onmyoji?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.28,0:18:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selain Tenyakuryo, ada juga biro Onmyoryo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.86,0:18:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu institusi khusus yang didedikasikan\Nuntuk astronomi dan kalender.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.24,0:18:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi pada era Heian,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.70,0:18:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kepercayaan pada kutukan yang disebabkan\Noleh roh pendendam dan iblis,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.54,0:18:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang dikenal sebagai Goryo Shinko,\Nmenyebar luas,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.75,0:18:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}menyebabkan penggunaan mantra Onmyodo\Nuntuk menangkal bencana
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.29,0:18:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan menyegel roh jahat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.34,0:18:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sementara itu, Jugondo dianggap berbahaya
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.38,0:18:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}karena insiden berulang\Nyang melibatkan Enmi dan kodoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.51,0:19:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, Tenyakuryo diserap ke dalam Onmyoryo
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.39,0:19:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan sistem Jugon dihapuskan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.73,0:19:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Diserap oleh Onmyoryo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.65,0:19:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mengenai Klan Goko yang kau sebutkan,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.19,0:19:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sekeras apa pun aku mencari,\Naku tidak bisa menemukan apa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.74,0:19:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin ini bukan waktu yang tepat\Nuntuk menanyai Mao soal ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.24,0:19:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau harus membunuh Nona Sana juga?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.95,0:19:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mao tampak lebih terguncang\Ndaripada biasanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.37,0:19:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa Nona Sana baginya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.80,0:19:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entah kenapa dia menyuruhku\Nmeneliti semua ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.30,0:19:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.05,0:19:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kamar Nanoka wangi sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.31,0:19:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Haimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.86,0:19:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Turunlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.36,0:19:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona Sana!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.57,0:19:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan menurunkannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.44,0:20:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hyakka.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.70,0:20:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo, Haimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.37,0:20:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Haimaru! Hentikan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.75,0:20:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Izinkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.34,0:20:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.76,0:20:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.85,0:20:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Haimaru benci disentuh\Noleh siapa pun kecuali aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.56,0:20:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Haimaru, kau suka Mao?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.44,0:20:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona Sana…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.70,0:20:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah kupikir-pikir, apa aku
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.53,0:20:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}diincar sejak awal?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.83,0:20:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka sudah bersih-bersih sedikit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.76,0:21:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kliniknya selamat dari kebakaran.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.76,0:21:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona Nanoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.64,0:21:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.27,0:21:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua orang sangat membantu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.52,0:21:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku merasa canggung bicara dengannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.82,0:21:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nanoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.20,0:21:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tak takut padaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.16,0:21:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Takut padamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.20,0:21:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meskipun aku tak ingat,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.12,0:21:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku mungkin telah membunuh putri Guru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.96,0:21:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mungkin telah membunuh Nona Sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.04,0:21:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika kau mengatakannya seperti itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.84,0:21:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kurasa aku takut, tapi…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.01,0:21:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku perlu tahu…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.59,0:21:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.22,0:21:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kalian berdua
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.35,0:21:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}pasangan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.43,0:21:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.48,0:21:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika kau mewarisi semua gulungan rahasia,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.27,0:22:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mao, itu artinya kau akan menjadi suamiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.94,0:22:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona Sana, kau bisa menerimanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.90,0:22:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan mematuhi keinginan ayahku.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.33,0:22:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi Nona Sana…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.00,0:22:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa aku menanyakan sesuatu\Nyang tidak seharusnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.39,0:22:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.77,0:22:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berbahaya berjalan sendirian\Ndi tempat seperti ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.06,0:22:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau tidak masuk?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.48,0:22:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak usah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.23,0:22:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mencari seseorang.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.53,0:22:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seorang pelayan memeriksa kerabat\Nyang tinggal di dekat sini
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.82,0:22:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan dia tidak pernah kembali.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.87,0:22:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada rumor
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.75,0:22:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bahwa beberapa wanita muda\Nmenghilang di area ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.04,0:23:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jadi, aku khawatir.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.34,0:23:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitukah?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.47,0:23:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga, wanita yang cantik.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.68,0:23:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa perjalanan ke sini sepadan.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.48,0:24:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejumlah
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.61,0:24:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}wanita muda menghilang.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.07,0:24:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku yakin pria itu yang bertanggung jawab.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.53,0:24:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau datang untuk membunuhku?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.79,0:25:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika Mao masih hidup,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.83,0:25:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}murid senior lainnya mungkin juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.08,0:25:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nanoka, tolong kemarilah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.42,0:25:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.46,0:25:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kodok raksasa itu bahkan tak punya pusar,\Ndan tongkatnya terlalu pendek!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.34,0:25:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku takut! Menjijikkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.13,0:25:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak bisa melakukannya! Tidak mungkin!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.18,0:25:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selanjutnya, "Kamon".
